# 015 — UX shell II: persistent environment/favorites, preferences, theme/dockable panels & validation (Part J §J.6–J.9)

## Spec reference

- `C:\GitHub\Berreman\specs\0022\.spec-md` — parent spec (Spec 0022, Berreman Optical Constructor — solution architecture & cross-cutting contract).
- Slice 001 (`.slices/001.slice-md`) — scaffold + the buildable FuncUI interpretation (public MIT `Avalonia.FuncUI` NuGet ≠ the audit-gated clone) every UI-touching slice relies on.
- Slice 003 (`.slices/003.slice-md`) — storage core: the Part I `serializeProject` shared `JsonSerializerOptions` (§I.1) this slice reuses for `EnvironmentSettings`.
